import React from 'react'
import { FeatureBody, FeatureHeader, FeatureRow, FeatureSection } from '../MainSection/FeaturesElements'
import NavigationBar from '../Navigation/NavigationBar'
import BarChart from './BarChart'
import StickyHeadTable from './FeedTables'
import LineChart from './LineChart'
import PieChart from './PieChart'

function DashBoard() {
    const dashBoard = {
        isDashBoard: true
    }

    return (
        <>
            <NavigationBar {...dashBoard} />
            <FeatureBody bgColor='#f4f4f4'>
                <FeatureSection>
                    <FeatureRow>
                        <FeatureHeader>Hi Bar Chart</FeatureHeader>
                        
                    </FeatureRow>
                </FeatureSection>
            </FeatureBody>
            <FeatureBody bgColor='#0F293D'>
                <LineChart bgColor='#f4f4f4' />
            </FeatureBody>
            <FeatureBody bgColor='#f4f4f4'>
                <PieChart bgColor='#0F293D' />
            </FeatureBody>
            <FeatureBody bgColor='#fff'>
                <FeatureSection>
                    <FeatureRow>
                        <FeatureHeader>Hi Table Chart</FeatureHeader>
                        <StickyHeadTable />
                    </FeatureRow>
                </FeatureSection>
            </FeatureBody>


        </>

    )
}

export default DashBoard
